      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i'm just running in circles. every time i think i finally got my life together, like actually stable, i just screw it all up again. the same mistakes, the same people, the same empty feeling. it's like i'm stuck in this loop and no matter how hard i try to break out, i just end up right back where i started. i'm just so tired of fighting the same battle every single day.",
